Package oracle.sdoapi.sref

Interface Summary
GeographicCS Interface for Geographic Coordinate Systems.
NonEarthCS Interface for Non-Earth Coordinate Systems.
ProjectedCS Interface for Projected coordinate Systems.
Projection Base interface for the transformation between GCS and PCS.
SpatialReference Interface for a spatial reference system.
SRManager The interface for managing spatial reference systems and transformations.
Transform Transforms geometry between spatial reference systems.
Unit  
 

Class Summary
AngularUnit This class defines commonly used angular units.
GeodeticDatum Represents the definition of a geodetic datum.
GeodeticEllipsoid Ellipsoid captures the shape and size of the earth.
LinearUnit A class representing linear measurement unit.
PrimeMeridian  
srsHolder Class srsHolder: Dummy placeholder for server side SRID and WKT information for later use (if necessary) by the client side coordinate system package that implements ProjectedCS, GeographicCS and Transform.
XFormParameters A catch-all structure for transformation parameters.
 

Exception Summary
SRException Spatial reference related exception.
